      <title>交易员等待通胀线索，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预期美国关键通胀指标将确认价格压力缓解，可能促使美联储在未来几个月内降息，全球股市小幅走高，美元回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/asian-stocks-set-to-slip-into-cpi-election-week-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 22:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾经像“瘟疫”一样被避之不及的新兴市场时长如今又重新流行起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/once-avoided-like-the-plague-em-duration-is-back-in-fashion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场债务的投资者再次转向长期债券，这是去年年底的一种流行押注，但许多投资者在 2024 年头几个月损失惨重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/once-avoided-like-the-plague-em-duration-is-back-in-fashion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
